<i>adjective</i>: 송연하다 [송ː연하다], 섬뜩하다 [섬뜨카다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>송연하다 [송ː연하다]</dt><br>
<dd>terrified; horrified</dd><br>
<dd>두려워 소름이 끼치는 듯하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling a shudder for fear of something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>섬뜩하다 [섬뜨카다]</dt><br>
<dd>terrified; frightened</dd><br>
<dd>갑자기 몹시 무섭고 불안하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being suddenly very scared and anxious.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>